body: 'If you planning for a solo tip for at least 12 to 15 days this is the best one with best volume but you planning for 1 week solo trip its a bit big.. I was really confused on the volume and size with 32cm && this 57 cm model and read lots of comments to clarify my doubt but was unclear on the volume and capacity then finally bought the 57cm model its little big for the exact size i wanted for solo 1 week trip but then the Quality and finish and color of the product is excellent.. .. So hope this will help the next person to choose their best trolly.. Thanks and Regards (Jeet Kumar Ghosh).... Safari is no doubt the best in build quality...'

'Not sturdy or smooth and smaller!'
body: Looks good but the zipper inside the compartment, makes a sound like it's tearing apart everytime you try to unzip. Apart from this, the main zip also looks very weak and difficult to open.  Also, the size of the product sent is close to 7 cms smaller than mentioned in the description. I'd to travel urgently so kept the bag. If I didn't have to catch a flight the next day, I'd have definitely returned it.
